    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>There is no Option to set the Plugin Directory like in my Example.</p>

<p>Application/Resource/FrontController.php:</p>

<p>protected $_pluginDir;
[...]
               case 'plugindirectory':
                    $_pluginDir = $value;
                    break;</p>

<pre><code>            case 'plugins':
                foreach ((array) $value as $key=&gt;$pluginClass) {
                    require_once $_pluginDir.'/'.$key.'.php';
                    $plugin = new $pluginClass();
                    $front-&gt;registerPlugin($plugin);
                }
                break;
</code></pre>

<p>[...]</p>

<p>*.ini
resources.frontController.plugindirectory = APPLICATION_PATH "/plugins"
resources.frontController.plugins.Acl = "Plugin_Acl"</p>

